<body>
    <h1>Case Escalation - Technical Requirements and Design</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"eac24289-7cbd-42b5-8a4a-1dc7b777ee9e" id=3D"CaseEsc=
alation-TechnicalRequirementsandDesign-Summary">
<style>[data-colorid=3Dwj9xts2ff6]{color:#ff991f} html[data-color-mode=3Dda=
rk] [data-colorid=3Dwj9xts2ff6]{color:#e07a00}[data-colorid=3Dnxoduv593m]{c=
olor:#ff991f} html[data-color-mode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dnxoduv593m]{colo=
r:#e07a00}[data-colorid=3Dzfzcigjvgv]{color:#ff991f} html[data-color-mode=
=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dzfzcigjvgv]{color:#e07a00}[data-colorid=3Dwcz5e2hn=
ux]{color:#ff991f} html[data-color-mode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dwcz5e2hnux]=
{color:#e07a00}[data-colorid=3Dnsbv9rckuc]{color:#ff991f} html[data-color-m=
ode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dnsbv9rckuc]{color:#e07a00}[data-colorid=3De2c7n=
glrne]{color:#ff991f} html[data-color-mode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3De2c7nglr=
ne]{color:#e07a00}</style>Summary</h1>
<p local-id=3D"794788d0e9c9">This document outlines the technical requireme=
nts and the design of a <strong>custom Case Escalation framework in NetSuit=
e </strong>to support the Collections Case Management.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f78adca1f211">Due to limitations in standard NetSuite escala=
tion functionality(Explained in detail <a href=3D"https://datacomgroup.atla=
ssian.net/wiki/spaces/ERPGT/pages/40934342812/Escalation+Options+Comparison=
" data-linked-resource-id=3D"40934342812" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1=
5" data-linked-resource-type=3D"page">here</a> ) a <strong>custom solution =
</strong>will be implemented.</p>
<p local-id=3D"776f5ba9ebfd">The solution is based on the principal:</p>
<p local-id=3D"a12f00b54eab" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;"><strong>Each Ca=
se Escalation record represents a single escalatee (internal ie within Coll=
ections team or External ie outside of collections team) and a single unit =
of responsibility.</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"4679d312a060">This ensures:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e7897a5a846f">
<li local-id=3D"a11c96a1cd59">
<p local-id=3D"248ac20be13b">Clear ownership</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b0bbd04d168">
<p local-id=3D"cd20625465d2">Controlled Notifications</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f427e3a86e17">
<p local-id=3D"7a48d80d2ede">Independent lifecycle tracking</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"269f55cdf274">
<p local-id=3D"8ec27d49b2c2">Strong Auditability</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"dfcf89d35322"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"7a81d1ed-94ee-4d12-ac0a-dcff78de1525" id=3D"CaseEscalation-=
TechnicalRequirementsandDesign-Assumptions">Assumptions</h2>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"7a65b373ebf2">
<li local-id=3D"80db704d9213">
<p local-id=3D"fb4d6a449464">Case Record exists prior to escalation creatio=
n</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3a1b7ff81a4c">
<p local-id=3D"f39919fb8718">Multiple escalations will be recorded per case=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"93bafa305297">
<p local-id=3D"05ded4460644">Each escalation is a single unit of work and a=
ssigned to one escalatee only</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"931b117d20ce">
<p local-id=3D"22b7c6b2ae77">External escalatees do not access/update the c=
ase or escalations records</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa4a1748a804">
<p local-id=3D"3ea77edc4ca2">External escalatees refers to Datacom Employee=
s outside of collections team</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6818204b75a">
<p local-id=3D"3e3330408687">Internal escalatees refers to Employees within=
 the Datacom Collections Team</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"baf145454450">
<p local-id=3D"3a8402c290d1">Internal escalatees receive notification on cr=
eation of escalation ONLY</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4e5293b9df00">
<p local-id=3D"28ad7c68f71b">Cases will only be escalated to Employees and =
<strong>NO </strong>other entities like Vendors, Customers etc</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 local-id=3D"1ea748f7ce24" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-InScope">In Scope</h2>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"21a18dfd184a">
<li local-id=3D"2625c4c8163b">
<p local-id=3D"96a50912f292">Creation and Management of<strong> multiple ca=
se escalation records per case</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b884edccbab0">
<p local-id=3D"9b297c3eec83">Each Escalation assigned to one escalatee only=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a1f165a4c2c6">
<p local-id=3D"0bb409e98010">Support for:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"841fa8e35bc1">
<li local-id=3D"d3c09df56362">
<p local-id=3D"6c4f2cef2f09">Internal escalations (with notifications)</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"cefaa4bb9d21">
<p local-id=3D"7c41bea81884">External escalations (No notifications)</p></l=
i>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"3eec24514a38">
<p local-id=3D"fd33ccd0b71f">Response tracking via</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"07e7e13c8526">
<li local-id=3D"1ca8504d97ce">
<p local-id=3D"4b6e69b0a96e">Case&gt; Communication &gt; Messages(full comm=
unication)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e015c9b57ff5">
<p local-id=3D"c556cb1cfd9f">Escalation Response records(structured audit)<=
/p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"c02c9583efde">
<p local-id=3D"e30a5fa4c8c4">Escalation Lifecycle management</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"39eda86ed43d">
<p local-id=3D"e55954ca9938">De-escalation with mandatory reason</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d49f97e784e7">
<p local-id=3D"ba5886601147">Reporting and audit trail</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 local-id=3D"27b3e7780b31" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-OutofScope">Out of Scope</h2>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"fc8b3f9f6b4d">
<li local-id=3D"cfbee1db3109">
<p local-id=3D"d24f18d36f39">External Email communication with the external=
 escalatees will not be tracked via case record or case escalation record.<=
/p></li>
</ol>
<h1 local-id=3D"bc5fe6b9-1cde-4f44-819b-a30e17a1afa8" id=3D"CaseEscalation-=
TechnicalRequirementsandDesign-EscalationProcess">Escalation Process</h1>
<h5 local-id=3D"4e0f89b8f5bb" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-CustomRecordStructure">Custom Record Structure</h5><span class=3D"co=
nfluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=
=3D"confluence-embedded-image confluence-external-resource" height=3D"440" =
width=3D"440" src=3D"a4436569eb5ac307874baff2c6cd1eef173cf57539e78fa4fec187=
3fffeb0e28" data-image-src=3D"/wiki/download/attachments/40934604889/Untitl=
ed%20Diagram-1774950328595.drawio.png?api=3Dv2" loading=3D"lazy"></span>
<h5 local-id=3D"74ba2b487529" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-EscalationProcess.1"><strong>Escalation Process</strong></h5><span c=
lass=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><=
img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image confluence-external-resource" height=
=3D"348" width=3D"468" src=3D"cbb4ba32936729bd5b52fe91cbe0ed7e33209edec4408=
dff86a3c1a8d1b36d26" data-image-src=3D"/wiki/download/attachments/409346048=
89/Untitled%20Diagram-1774920144007.drawio.png?api=3Dv2" loading=3D"lazy"><=
/span>
<h5 local-id=3D"65c2a2b3939a" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-AddResponsestoEscalations"><strong>Add Responses to Escalations</str=
ong></h5><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedde=
d-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image confluence-external-=
resource" height=3D"314" width=3D"166" src=3D"d4b894ef05c7ac0b6c0c85d6fd503=
cccb775197a7dd07b032e38946939e8a942" data-image-src=3D"/wiki/download/attac=
hments/40934604889/Untitled%20Diagram-1774950875909.drawio.png?api=3Dv2" lo=
ading=3D"lazy"></span>
<h5 local-id=3D"a1a90be13d75" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-De-escalationProcess">De-escalation Process</h5><span class=3D"confl=
uence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"=
confluence-embedded-image confluence-external-resource" height=3D"684" widt=
h=3D"352" src=3D"46201a80987171983a6d49cd9c00aa1551590760eebcb0d12a088e3856=
32572f" data-image-src=3D"/wiki/download/attachments/40934604889/Untitled%2=
0Diagram-1774995050652.drawio.png?api=3Dv2" loading=3D"lazy"></span>
<h2 local-id=3D"56cb50ad-e01a-4afb-808d-862e0de31ef4" id=3D"CaseEscalation-=
TechnicalRequirementsandDesign-Process">Process</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"8c=
627dab-d4b6-4076-86a1-56cc0a032d71" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 208.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 552.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1b31eab7-f13e-4dba-ab3f-56009289428b">
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"fd70f9f9-e378-49f4-8=
731-7d8389f5fcdd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8e5d68fa6a3e"><strong>Goal</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"38d0c131-8e92-4a45-bc9d-9b9ac1a82bf9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f6724bc17a54">Allowing the case assignee to escalate cases t=
o Internal(Within Collections team) and External(Outside of Collections tea=
m) escalatees by :</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"7b0b0bee6852">
<li local-id=3D"bec43b11c328">
<p local-id=3D"a98b3f7e3f5a">Enabling clear ownership per escalation</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"2916d2699a8b">
<p local-id=3D"80e648dc8f0e">Supporting multiple independent escalations</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"c5fffbeefe8b">
<p local-id=3D"93323bf84ed6">Control notifications(internal only)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4874681386a">
<p local-id=3D"44b1e339da7f">Providing structured audit trail</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d5e6d327de24">
<p local-id=3D"1cec0410b0e0">Ensuring scalability and reporting capability<=
/p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8cd9ee7c-928b-4b8e-bc10-73db8928533b">
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"ba205471-41cc-47f1-a=
614-76fd67a01f86" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"79800cfe4f69"><strong>Business Rules</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ec8530bc-72b1-4cff-bc4d-549d3c9638bb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"77c7f16af366">
<li local-id=3D"0479d45a49c1">
<p local-id=3D"510d8821105d">Each escalation must have <strong>one escalate=
e only</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2b7b9319d514">
<p local-id=3D"8b35628997bb">Escalation type</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"96c5640f682a">
<li local-id=3D"88da751e7b78">
<p local-id=3D"ba66d8d3e661">Internal =3D Within collections team</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9303dd658431">
<p local-id=3D"b34d29c5a4f8">External =3D Outside of collections team</p></=
li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"4311a5016751">
<p local-id=3D"93c1a51da0ab">Internal escalatees receive notifications on c=
reation of escalation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"baa490c815dc">
<p local-id=3D"64a8cde11079">External escalatees do NOT receive notificatio=
ns</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4b50edc98e2f">
<p local-id=3D"256ac9fa44b2">Multiple escalations allowed per case</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d5af5c76f205">
<p local-id=3D"0770f5c4e65f">De-escalation requires a <strong>mandatory rea=
son</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c049372a21e3">
<p local-id=3D"c023d00aeba5">Case is escalated if <strong>any escalation is=
 active</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ab9356c86d77">
<p local-id=3D"e10bbb6ba909">Case is de-escalated only if all escalations a=
re descalated</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8d724b97-a4fe-4a3f-ba7c-89dccc1ceb70">
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"7446bfbf-e693-44cf-8=
33b-a5421e0da024" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"09d3eecc7e03"><strong>Business event / Trigger</strong></p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1c40cfd0-ee94-4b83-800f-e8065e457101" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"9aa43810c99a">
<li local-id=3D"dff3fa6f4ab7">
<p local-id=3D"ad4a754455c3">Case Escalation created</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"397242221894">
<p local-id=3D"bc82b2a5070e">Case Escalation updated</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c827f3ab22a">
<p local-id=3D"9edc3822d530">Escalation Response recorded</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"75b39ff612e4">
<p local-id=3D"4a6906ca5961">Case Escalation closed</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1ec9d46e-0eb1-4ed3-a27c-1a381007a50b">
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"adf4ae91-43c4-4876-a=
674-711b623c531b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"96ef9e1e076d"><strong>Frequency</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"71c4c55e-af08-47a9-9bf6-2dcdf2636384" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bfe4d8d0b8e4"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8405cf15-be89-4843-b52f-1decd3e923de">
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"e845371d-1ee7-44b6-b=
318-ffa7a9fcb4f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a3f27fe7e7e0"><strong>Actor(s)</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"abf956fc-7cf0-4eb2-a998-c97350103b73" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<ul local-id=3D"26752f18-62e2-43e8-8a87-316a403c71e1">
<li local-id=3D"4285f435-cef7-4d06-ab01-2796da85b39a">
<p local-id=3D"ce3bd691516c">NetSuite (System)</p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"de1dbf75-dfb5-4bdb-80e1-0baab214b02b">
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"a04897b4-89da-470d-a=
612-1435d120f850" class=3D"confluenceTd">
