<h1 local-id=3D"df6ac3b52c7b" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-DataModel">Data Model</h1>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"444986e4286a">
<li local-id=3D"cb51ace205af">
<p local-id=3D"cd02f099c835">Custom Record: Case Escalation Record</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3c8bb2bb1c58">
<p local-id=3D"6e5576986f14">Custom Record: Case Escalation Response</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"042646f956cf">
<p local-id=3D"38612e59eded">Workflow: Validations on creation of Case Esca=
lation Record and controlling the escalation lifecycle</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb8ebccc0fad">
<p local-id=3D"f43ff19b87c7">Workflow Action Script:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"01d5e2f34d5f">
<li local-id=3D"03151f6310cd">
<p local-id=3D"33a552c06ba1">To set the Parent Case Record status to =E2=80=
=9CEscalated=E2=80=9D when there is atleast 1 child case escalation record.=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"664393eff94c">
<p local-id=3D"edb54a9ddd5d">To set the Parent Case Record status to =E2=80=
=9CIn-Progress=E2=80=9D when there are no child case escalation record.</p>=
</li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"43c1dd0e8ed2">
<p local-id=3D"aa7884fe7352">Workflow Action Script:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"deb803e646a1">
<li local-id=3D"404da937f1a1">
<p local-id=3D"7628809bef51">To sent out escalation email notifications to =
the internal escalatee if the escalation type =3D Internal</p></li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
<h1 local-id=3D"1f5eae64-5cef-4be2-9632-38b043492eed" id=3D"CaseEscalation-=
TechnicalRequirementsandDesign-SolutionDesign">Solution Design</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"417a7be45ca8" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-CustomRecords">Custom Records</h3>
<h5 local-id=3D"df8ed8542067" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-CaseEscalation"><span data-colorid=3D"nsbv9rckuc">Case Escalation</s=
pan></h5>
<p local-id=3D"b013e53a3676">Custom Record to record escalations for cases.=
 There can be multiple case escalations recorded against a case</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"4a=
7b463d6edd" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col style=3D"width: 583.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 177.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"df1de5fc-6a60-4617-b2ce-e14a01e5275e">
<th class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTh"></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"5e70f3fa-c974-4438-9=
eed-2a00b30db6d7" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"53c0b84f158e"><strong>Description</strong></p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"7a4e5cbe-6c16-44d5-b=
f56-6d00fd1f28ae" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5d8ec477055a"><strong>Jira</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"509210eb-2298-4a21-b13f-83b31a0ca5b4">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd">1</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fce7bf2e-c411-4c66-adf3-98c8341b1775" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"90c0b72a8847" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-CE_TR01:EscalationRecord">CE_TR01: Escalation Record</h4>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"96ecfa567b64">
<li local-id=3D"6e302169e709">
<p local-id=3D"ac9c3ec4c0e0">Create a custom list <strong>=E2=80=9CEscalati=
on Type List=E2=80=9D</strong> with the following values</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e0822d96f193">
<li local-id=3D"2834dd3ce8b7">
<p local-id=3D"a55ae14c17f1">Internal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a30aaaae950">
<p local-id=3D"9a036e24076d">External</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"051ff5048d20">
<p local-id=3D"69950dcb5fef">Create a custom list <strong>=E2=80=9CEscalati=
on Status=E2=80=9D</strong> with the following values:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"1fb45988cd43">
<li local-id=3D"50cdc59fa6fe">
<p local-id=3D"db36320a64ae">Not Escalated</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ab9699defff5">
<p local-id=3D"468de9a9e963">Escalated</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4c7a38e14364">
<p local-id=3D"3a5acb36fe74">De-escalated</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"56aecda6e962">
<p local-id=3D"9324a01c68b8">Create a custom record <strong>=E2=80=9CCase E=
scalation=E2=80=9D</strong> as child record of Case for recording escalatio=
ns for a case.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0d8afcbf1825">
<p local-id=3D"945f3f3f1cc2"><strong>The =E2=80=9CCase Escalation=E2=80=9D =
</strong>custom record should have the following fields</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"b6d897f559aa">
<li local-id=3D"9846c3ef5214">
<p local-id=3D"42859959b1e9">Parent Case</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"aac88ca7ecc8">
<li local-id=3D"a2ffd85c91d0">
<p local-id=3D"724e037513a3">Mandatory: Yes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f35922ac409f">
<p local-id=3D"588347e0b98a">Type: List/Record =E2=86=92 Case</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"629c1eafdaa8">
<p local-id=3D"b189d1540bd7">Display: Inline</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dd577f906a47">
<p local-id=3D"e8f6a3d878f5">Description: The parent case id of the escalat=
ion record</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"783b9432565e">
<p local-id=3D"e2d880b5a77d">Escalation Type:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8a217e456d7b">
<li local-id=3D"722c6e77eff1">
<p local-id=3D"651c43e3b6e8">Mandatory: Yes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a2db419e4578">
<p local-id=3D"d84fb9a08d3b">Type: List/Record -&gt;Escalation Type List(Cu=
stom LIst)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"379615af922a">
<p local-id=3D"3eabd4c21332">Display: Normal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f454a67b99d">
<p local-id=3D"540c785b94d2">Description: Denotes if the escalation is to i=
nternal or external escalatees</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"580d3cafcf53">
<p local-id=3D"c4e954f2cace">Internal Escalatee</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"1ba5b6866552">
<li local-id=3D"f86accf74ea3">
<p local-id=3D"2b634f5b4193">Mandatory:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"419122e3f17f">
<li local-id=3D"e1c7de707e3a">
<p local-id=3D"b89127fc6ffe">Yes: if the escalation type =3D internal</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"1ef1c10f3078">
<p local-id=3D"7b6d35cee602">No: If the escalation type =3D external</p></l=
i>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb9afe8f4895">
<p local-id=3D"abc10328ca7e">Type: List/Record =E2=86=92 Employee</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c64ead0f4df7">
<p local-id=3D"407e4631fde5">Display(Controlled by workflow):</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"a260ba69edd4">
<li local-id=3D"10902b84262e">
<p local-id=3D"e73a0dd1e41b">Inline: if the escalation type is =E2=80=9CExt=
ernal=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c72fd47c7479">
<p local-id=3D"783c598ba6d0">Normal: If the Escalation type is =E2=80=9CInt=
ernal=E2=80=9D</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"915490e46164">
<p local-id=3D"e8e417c87dcc">Sourcing and Filtering: Add a filter to source=
 only Employees who have the role =E2=80=9C Datacom Credit Controller=E2=80=
=9D or =E2=80=9CDatacom A/R Collections Manager=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fe8be8e35065">
<p local-id=3D"136728e924f0">Description: This field holds the internal esc=
alatee the case will be escalated to. This field will be editable only if t=
he escalation type is =E2=80=9CInternal=E2=80=9D</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"68f843b397fd">
<p local-id=3D"f284a90b3774">External Escalatee:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"3c1d68e8c790">
<li local-id=3D"f5a60ebdd60d">
<p local-id=3D"1662b2205f0a">Mandatory:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"6eb3d90c2431">
<li local-id=3D"197b227f7854">
<p local-id=3D"f52f74370dbb">Yes: if the escalation type is =E2=80=9Cextern=
al=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c25420e5403d">
<p local-id=3D"694aabcf9111">No: If the escalation type is =E2=80=9Cinterna=
l=E2=80=9D</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"7b1e3a089322">
<p local-id=3D"5c1f74acb9ab">Type: List/Record =E2=86=92 Employee</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4f4382ac6609">
<p local-id=3D"cdec98719cc0">Display</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"2beb1d7942cb">
<li local-id=3D"ddc518392f57">
<p local-id=3D"1026ae231aed">Inline: If the escalation type is =E2=80=9CInt=
ernal=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca3f0d37e014">
<p local-id=3D"4bcac546a265">Normal: If the escalation type is =E2=80=9CExt=
ernal=E2=80=9D</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"08c45533de30">
<p local-id=3D"fc2047e6fe60">Sourcing and Filtering: Add a filter to source=
 only Employees who do NOT have the role =E2=80=9C Datacom Credit Controlle=
r=E2=80=9D or =E2=80=9CDatacom A/R Collections Manager=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f7f06f7932be">
<p local-id=3D"0a47da5527fa">Description: This field holds the external esc=
alatee the case will be escalated to. This field will be editable only if t=
he escalation type is =E2=80=9CExternal=E2=80=9D</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"eb613d32ca7b">
<p local-id=3D"05b7829425c8">Escalation Status:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"68fc0db372ec">
<li local-id=3D"169633bca0f0">
<p local-id=3D"574d8edaaa6e">Mandatory: Yes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce4c9eb1ede4">
<p local-id=3D"8f77426c1823">Type: List/Record =E2=86=92<strong> =E2=80=9CE=
scalation Status=E2=80=9D(custom list)</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3d5b27dea784">
<p local-id=3D"455cb24b38d5">Display: Inline</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f64e99d65787">
<p local-id=3D"baf0d4586001">Description: Denotes the status of the escalat=
ion, if its escalated or de-escalated.</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"5badabdaaab4">
<p local-id=3D"ea8036083a4a">Escalation Message:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"03b313ae74ad">
<li local-id=3D"b7ee46945ffd">
<p local-id=3D"cfc307df8475">Mandatory: Yes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8cd1e99b6466">
<p local-id=3D"ae72e8a5a988">Type: Text</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fc0296a45d27">
<p local-id=3D"131d20afc16d">Display: Normal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"de0649423223">
<p local-id=3D"7d0ade98d1a4">Description: This field denotes the escalation=
 reason/message</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"50daaf6a0d81">
<p local-id=3D"7f57f8538f46">De-escalation Reason:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"a2bae1f5c694">
<li local-id=3D"0ce78264bf50">
<p local-id=3D"e30d54421413">Mandatory: Controlled through customization</p=
>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"64946f0a0894">
<li local-id=3D"3a322db4f56b">
<p local-id=3D"7de4e84306c3">Yes: If the escalation status is =E2=80=9CDe-e=
scalated=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"92ef5994a792">
<p local-id=3D"6c08354cc847">No: If the escalation status is =E2=80=9CEscal=
ated</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"cf982482b3b0">
<p local-id=3D"de97d437f02c">Display: Normal</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"07d92daf6eb4">
<p local-id=3D"50593f5bce12">Escalation Start Date</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"f653393bc2a6">
<li local-id=3D"3e960147f922">
<p local-id=3D"56db2059ae6d">Mandatory: Yes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fcd9e2a89eae">
<p local-id=3D"e3b15b94cee4">Type: Date</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c7dfa531a61">
<p local-id=3D"3e46073aa219">Display: Normal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22bfb32c4595">
<p local-id=3D"3d64835b03be">Defaulting: Defaulted to today=E2=80=99s date<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b663494178e8">
<p local-id=3D"c7249f53b968">Description: The start date of the escalation<=
/p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"bcc788e9e163">
<p local-id=3D"f42067ec761e">Escalation End Date:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d4d037f7843b">
<li local-id=3D"1d4bfceb848a">
<p local-id=3D"406e935528bc">Mandatory: No</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e20aee0057d1">
<p local-id=3D"9d2238e853a1">Type: Date</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7e32448a2a0b">
<p local-id=3D"edec524deaed">Display: Inline</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"19709d69ffe0">
<p local-id=3D"eae69c1aa694">Description: Automatically entered on clicking=
 de-escalate button</p></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"5573034629ab"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"aa10f5fe-fea8-4e19-9ea9-913f66e7e76a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"076c93f986b2">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h5 local-id=3D"078bb61e4625" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-CaseEscalationResponse"><span data-colorid=3D"wcz5e2hnux">Case Escal=
ation Response</span></h5>
<p local-id=3D"22e06e282850">Child record of case escalation custom record =
to record responses from escalatees</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"55=
ac1347bc64" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col style=3D"width: 583.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 177.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5b5c6173-9f31-4378-8be2-131341b8bcb0">
<th class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTh"></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"033d0179-6a90-43fb-8=
a43-93854b4d1dd7" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"03cb1d60e793"><strong>Description</strong></p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"fcbbe344-dd9d-4b2b-a=
c49-d48348c5e4ce" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"ee49c8a41a57"><strong>Jira</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f21a2252-891b-4c1a-a7e4-2828d3c5cccb">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd">1</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dc6885b6fc04" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"37d96bcd5709" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-CE_TR02:CaseEscalationResponse">CE_TR02: Case Escalation Response</h=
4>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"aa463b449824">
<li local-id=3D"3d709eb5598e">
<p local-id=3D"048058ae50c8">Create custom record <strong>=E2=80=9CCase Esc=
alation Response=E2=80=9D</strong> as child record of the custom record =E2=
=80=9CCase Escalation=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5e5cebca81f">
<p local-id=3D"a0f47a181b0f">The <strong>=E2=80=9CCase Escalation Response=
=E2=80=9D </strong>should have the following fields:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"74a3338eb324">
<li local-id=3D"dbb06c76e117">
<p local-id=3D"7d7acf0912c0">Case Escalation</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"7501bea26e34">
<li local-id=3D"b723ea8ef271">
<p local-id=3D"030c105d55ba">Mandatory: Yes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cd5601b0ec92">
<p local-id=3D"410a4ec493fe">Type: List/Record =E2=86=92 Case Escalation</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"35d286b8b812">
<p local-id=3D"d685247edde1">Display: Inline</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ea2c35d760d7">
<p local-id=3D"4c683a458e53">Description: Stored the parent case escalation=
 record id</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"7b4b066c6454">
<p local-id=3D"92da2824c196">Response Message:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"fe6e37c3e6b1">
<li local-id=3D"39ad0399b27e">
<p local-id=3D"c79110f330d3">Mandatory: Yes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f92d5f2393fd">
<p local-id=3D"dfc8af302529">Type: Text</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3e051bc3c74a">
<p local-id=3D"8f0171529d6b">Display: Normal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e8a7547c1099">
<p local-id=3D"27198914f023">Description: The field to record the response =
message</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"a2fa7c57c49e">
<p local-id=3D"8f46493d21f2">Response Date:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"917446739b91">
<li local-id=3D"3b80655ac1cd">
<p local-id=3D"2e373ea45dac">Mandatory: Yes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fc14e66f2288">
<p local-id=3D"673cdf467c22">Type: Date</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"58c5f2970f4b">
<p local-id=3D"487d6d5244ec">Display: Normal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e82be48f51cf">
<p local-id=3D"1bcfe0122d18">Default: Automatically default to today=E2=80=
=99s date</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"581ac357f19a">
<p local-id=3D"04ae6c5573ba">Description: The field to record the Response =
date</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"b71d04e850ac">
<p local-id=3D"0a72e23a2123">Posted by:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"65a2488673a8">
<li local-id=3D"b6a35c36f24b">
<p local-id=3D"668903d2158e">Mandatory: No</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f1665de53356">
<p local-id=3D"94170b3f428c">Type: List/Record-&gt; Employee</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b731fa970ec7">
<p local-id=3D"93634fc99078">Display: Inline</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7d4a3eb71840">
<p local-id=3D"d9012cb33fec">Default: Defaulted to user creating the record=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e3938c0fc516">
<p local-id=3D"fd3e8278bff2">Description: The employee entering the comment=
s</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"a7c7833e8575">
<p local-id=3D"4a9e1483374f">On behalf of:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"22ba336fce85">
<li local-id=3D"89fa5210-6334-4c59-a137-fd697459b5db">
<p local-id=3D"d2b0da593a5e">Mandatory: No</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ac1f9e3c-a446-4224-9f03-df5d109a21a7">
<p local-id=3D"8f8dedff05d5">Type: List/Record-&gt; Employee</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cdcbe5a1-d055-4307-b068-4c6851ae6c06">
<p local-id=3D"d067ab7358c2">Display: Normal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"43fd4844-9068-4078-9a49-2efcfc5854d1">
<p local-id=3D"999b9ab0d875">Description: Update this field if the Posted b=
y is different from the person who has provided the response from the busin=
ess.</p></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5d5a186e-ffa5-41b9-bcba-a1c4a970635d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"805f776a9ef5">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
