<tr data-local-id=3D"9e3abf24-e224-48b1-98a5-1054f1ade82a">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd">1</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bdbda619-b0be-4c0d-86fd-a6663d2ce382" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"20616f5c305b" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-CE_TR04:CaseEscalationRecordValidationandLifecycle">CE_TR04: Case Es=
calation Record Validation and Lifecycle</h4>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e78ca57a-a970-4f7e-acca-cf20dd088191">
<li local-id=3D"dbc6fb04-2df6-4b58-a654-2ad40986c4bf">
<p local-id=3D"9e8473b9f58e">When the <strong>Escalation Type =3D Internal<=
/strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"263ca1a8-6684-4d9f-a7b4-77c5558d6071">
<li local-id=3D"9ece2070-28d9-4abf-954d-1c16b3337312">
<p local-id=3D"edee6b902eff">The Internal Escalatee should be set to DISPLA=
Y =3D Normal and Mandatory</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2b04a9aa-3143-458a-9e69-4901c867b162">
<p local-id=3D"5aedb40c2741">The External Escalatee should beset to DISPLAY=
 =3D DISABLED and non-mandatory</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7c5d759f-50eb-4d08-ab8c-020bb3b0c3e6">
<p local-id=3D"268ccb47a3e2">Clear External Escalatee field if it has value=
s</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"15632658-8327-4ad8-8e25-8aac1ad87e6a">
<p local-id=3D"e3c310390e52">When the <strong>Escalation Type =3D External<=
/strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"cf8b0291-bbdc-4cc8-953e-9fc34c97a69e">
<li local-id=3D"5cfe2a9d-c4e5-4a2b-9236-e7a1eaacfa91">
<p local-id=3D"05bd596655f2">The External Escalatee should be set to DISPLA=
Y =3D Normal and Mandatory</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"59785aaf-c8b0-43cf-b315-f5decffe3efa">
<p local-id=3D"5ae07df15c93">The Internal Escalatee should beset to DISPLAY=
 =3D DISABLED and non-mandatory</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"530f4b5f-9e0d-45eb-96a4-6f0a06efcea1">
<p local-id=3D"99c2af96b12b">Clear internal escalatee field if it has value=
s</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"9dc7fa92-c3e5-44ed-bba8-6a7bd153d06c">
<p local-id=3D"214ea5facb59"><strong>The Escalation Lifecycle</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8ff29a18-39e0-43da-b8a0-34900d45032f">
<li local-id=3D"8626ee5c-ccdd-4075-b704-fb495108edc8">
<p local-id=3D"dc7a2cf0e479">On Creation of Case Escalation Record</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"df3a1f18-b7f5-4cba-bf19-1c7d8840689a">
<li local-id=3D"a03f819b-ff74-40c3-bc26-176114ff68a5">
<p local-id=3D"fddd9aed5250">The escalation status should be set to =E2=80=
=9CNot Escalated=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"378b5d3f-a5de-4161-b2a0-3de123e3210b">
<p local-id=3D"cc9abd8780a5">If the escalation message is not entered throw=
 an error</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c332e34c-909a-4908-ae43-eab45ad7e734">
<p local-id=3D"d8fec574697c">The <strong>escalate </strong>button should be=
 available on save</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"3e2618f6-4eca-430f-8071-1b9daf5ced6e">
<p local-id=3D"9420c0aee6bb">On Clicking the <strong>Escalate </strong>butt=
on</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"9799158d7757">
<li local-id=3D"16bb53742d0c">
<p local-id=3D"156c88aa70ae">the escalation status should be set to =E2=80=
=9CEscalated=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff4d61c5fc43">
<p local-id=3D"b311cc43cf64">The <a href=3D"https://datacomgroup.atlassian.=
net/wiki/spaces/ERPGT/pages/40934604889/Case+Escalation+-+Technical+Require=
ments+and+Design#CE_TR06%3A-Updates-to-Case-Record-status-field-when-case-i=
s-escalated-and-de-escalated" rel=3D"nofollow">Workflow Action Script</a> t=
o be called to set parent case record status to escalated( if not already e=
scalated).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c3735d6ea899">
<p local-id=3D"d15ed238daef">If the escalation type =3D Internal</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8c7e44256149">
<li local-id=3D"98e5ad9997aa">
<p local-id=3D"8ff2510f8c36"><a href=3D"https://datacomgroup.atlassian.net/=
wiki/spaces/ERPGT/pages/40934604889/Case+Escalation+-+Technical+Requirement=
s+and+Design#CE_TR06%3A-TO-send-out-email-notifications-to-external-escalat=
ees-on-case-escalation-record-creation" rel=3D"nofollow">Workflow Action Sc=
ript</a> to be called to send out email notification to the external escala=
tee</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"7d660814efdc">
<p local-id=3D"74bc18480c34">the de-escalate button should be visible</p></=
li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"04943214-b122-4543-b7d0-aebc4da7e42f">
<p local-id=3D"8569998ee392">On clicking the de-escalate button</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"0453f0a40ff6">
<li local-id=3D"3e687d5f7711">
<p local-id=3D"9156d0d46cf4">There should be a validation to check the de-e=
scalation message. If de-escalation message not entered then throw error</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"065857ec-633b-4794-9ef2-6ed3a651ee9b">
<p local-id=3D"4982071e69d5">If de-escalation message is entered then on cl=
icking de-escalate button the escalation status should be set to De-escalat=
ed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"246e1dc8-d73f-46fd-b398-db72e2450404">
<p local-id=3D"6b12695d1222">On clicking the de-escalate button set the Esc=
alation end date to todays date.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"792eb242ac3a">
<p local-id=3D"366c7f6aba3e">Workflow action script to be triggered to set =
the Parent Case to De-escalated if all the existing escalations are in de-e=
scalated status.(<a href=3D"https://datacomgroup.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/=
ERPGT/pages/40934604889/Case+Escalation+-+Technical+Requirements+and+Design=
#CE_TR06%3A-Updates-to-Case-Record-status-field-when-case-is-escalated-and-=
de-escalated" rel=3D"nofollow">here</a> )</p></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"c824e6cd1086"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ddb0628e-5abf-47c9-ab65-3c31b6fdbbe5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1f392745e191">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"58016333530e" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-Scripts">Scripts</h3>
<h5 local-id=3D"93386a72b360" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-WorkflowActionScript:CaseEscalationRecordtoupdateparentcaserecord"><=
span data-colorid=3D"e2c7nglrne">Workflow Action Script: Case Escalation Re=
cord to update parent case record</span></h5>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"6e=
9b8249528e" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col style=3D"width: 583.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 177.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c37c6f0e-89e8-46f2-aaaa-4edcce78d983">
<th class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTh"></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"6fc07b0c-2d6f-4719-b=
901-ff9292a08629" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"213681645764"><strong>Description</strong></p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"2afd0fee-f34e-48a7-b=
005-27d5abcccdbc" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"db25364cc650"><strong>Jira</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3e664cdf-9746-4c95-9e68-6fa782b386bb">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd">1</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d9d5aa67-1b0e-4e1e-b503-44371cf5e939" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"9e3ed76ff353" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-CE_TR05:UpdatestoCaseRecordstatusfieldwhencaseisescalatedandde-escal=
ated">CE_TR05: Updates to Case Record status field when case is escalated a=
nd de-escalated</h4>
<p local-id=3D"80a445c058d2"><strong>Type</strong>: Workflow action script<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"0fb26540fa26"><strong>Purpose</strong>:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ad89ddc594c2">
<li local-id=3D"5d4b1a32074c">
<p local-id=3D"385040d66be1">Set the Parent Case Record to =E2=80=9C<strong=
>Escalated</strong>=E2=80=9D if atleast one of the child case escalation re=
cords is set to escalated status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"da16db868a31">
<p local-id=3D"b4da95bb6c83">Set the Parent Case Record to =E2=80=9C<strong=
>In Progress</strong>=E2=80=9D only if all of the child case escalation rec=
ords are set to De-escalated status.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"96e57fbd29c0"><strong>Deploy</strong>: Escalation Case Recor=
d</p>
<p local-id=3D"dac19ae694d6"><strong>Triggers (</strong><a href=3D"https://=
datacomgroup.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/ERPGT/pages/40934604889/Case+Escalat=
ion+-+Technical+Requirements+and+Design#CE_TR04%3A-Case-Escalation-Record-V=
alidation-and-Lifecycle" rel=3D"nofollow">Workflow</a> ):</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"77f8106507ae">
<li local-id=3D"586570ecd6ad">
<p local-id=3D"44e0aa441e8a">On clicking =E2=80=9CEscalate=E2=80=9D button<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"40aa56fb592d">
<p local-id=3D"a632c14f45d0">On clicking =E2=80=9CDe-escalate=E2=80=9D butt=
on</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"d27f65f57e61"><strong>Logic</strong>:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ad7e59080f8a">
<li local-id=3D"6a4b46bba75b">
<p local-id=3D"5dc3d8574c86">Get the Parent_Case_Record.id</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"339e17e9302e">
<p local-id=3D"97e4473bc19a">Search if there are any case escalation record=
s with the parent case record id(#1) that are in escalated status</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"f78f689cb216">
<li local-id=3D"ec3852506ccb">
<p local-id=3D"1ee8a232dd63">Filters: Case_Escalation_Record.Parent_Case_id=
 =3D parent id from #1</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"410f0ca3ca62">
<p local-id=3D"aea40df86815">Case_Escalation_Record.Status =3D Escalated</p=
></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"058fee63aedd">
<p local-id=3D"68729437cf97">Get the count of case escalation records retur=
ned from the search in #2.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b211923e8a7a">
<p local-id=3D"e9de42d5841f">Load the Parent Case Record</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"243fa5f995a3">
<p local-id=3D"6219858a4906"><strong>IF </strong>search count from #3 &gt;0=
(ie if there are child case escalation records in escalated status) THEN</p=
>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"537835fa9e3a">
<li local-id=3D"ab608dda8b68">
<p local-id=3D"2522c75f8594">If Parent_Case_Record.Status !=3D =E2=80=9CEsc=
alated=E2=80=9D THEN</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"f57a420761b7">
<li local-id=3D"3437d6710cbd">
<p local-id=3D"4566e5b42195">Set Parent_Case_Record.Status to Escalated</p>=
</li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"1e5ec40d-0430-4f9b-b792-c4ab04f00281">
<p local-id=3D"b7d3e4b2783b"><strong>ELSE</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"bcee26a45f6c">
<li local-id=3D"b50464e1b46a">
<p local-id=3D"5e31f83f7207">If Parent_Case_Record.Status =3D=3D =E2=80=9CE=
scalated=E2=80=9D</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"989a69e24946">
<li local-id=3D"18db3973-dcd6-4f57-bae2-0c9f5cfbd3fd">
<p local-id=3D"77e712e9dd62">Set Parent_Case_Record.Status to =E2=80=9CIn P=
rogress=E2=80=9D</p></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"dbe3472424a4"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2fde012c-6777-4fec-af86-cc550f4df6ac" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3bc48d4eaabe">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h5 local-id=3D"54da79b33308" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-WorkflowActionScript-Tosendoutemailnotificationstointernalescalatees=
"><span data-colorid=3D"zfzcigjvgv">Workflow Action Script - To send out em=
ail notifications to internal escalatees</span></h5>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"d4=
850897b516" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col style=3D"width: 583.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 177.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b50073ac-6884-4a7f-8825-4d6530569478">
<th class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTh"></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"5c44301c-ec35-4cab-9=
6fa-603bbd85135d" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"eb8ccb5c989f"><strong>Description</strong></p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"e6ddb999-edc5-4f53-a=
825-e66cc85cd17b" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d72f90e45283"><strong>Jira</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e65b1b83-d160-4b41-9758-d7d2fb7788a4">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd">1</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e9b5147c-f8fc-4eb1-82f3-17601f95dfe9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"1f895e66ef0f" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-CE_TR06:Tosendoutemailnotificationstointernalescalateesoncaseescalat=
ionrecordcreation">CE_TR06: To send out email notifications to internal esc=
alatees on case escalation record creation</h4>
<p local-id=3D"fdfd6c52a7e6"><strong>Type</strong>: Workflow action script<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"d977de8fd401"><strong>Purpose</strong>:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"9f9995cb4502">
<li local-id=3D"b52baa293cba">
<p local-id=3D"be06c7c35548">If a case escalation is created for internal e=
scalation then the internal escalatee should be notified</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"02d3759f7f77"><strong>Deploy</strong>: Escalation Case Recor=
d</p>
<p local-id=3D"ec3b989481b6"><strong>Triggers</strong>:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"eaf5deb9-a94f-4c11-b9d4-208e5a4e71f9">
<li local-id=3D"f54deb41-cc1b-4278-a76f-0d7e8283a7fd">
<p local-id=3D"3b94421625a7">On clicking the escalate button in the workflo=
w<a data-card-appearance=3D"inline" href=3D"https://datacomgroup.atlassian.=
net/wiki/spaces/ERPGT/pages/40934604889/Case+Escalation+-+Technical+Require=
ments+and+Design#CE_TR05%3A-Case-Escalation-Record-Validation-and-Lifecycle=
" local-id=3D"aa6237745db3" rel=3D"nofollow">https://datacomgroup.atlassian=
.net/wiki/spaces/ERPGT/pages/40934604889/Case+Escalation+-+Technical+Requir=
ements+and+Design#CE_TR05%3A-Case-Escalation-Record-Validation-and-Lifecycl=
e</a></p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"25eda1cb7350"><strong>Logic</strong>:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"3dacdc80c64f">
<li local-id=3D"67f783edc268">
<p local-id=3D"054717325a15">Get the Case Escalation Type, Escalation Messa=
ge and Parent Case form the case escalation record.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2d77fc909708">
<p local-id=3D"e0a8a21cc00f">If the Escalation Type =3D Internal</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"048215af8ca3">
<li local-id=3D"986090263d3d">
<p local-id=3D"462184a2cd2e">Read the escalation email template (<a data-ca=
rd-appearance=3D"inline" href=3D"https://datacomgroup.atlassian.net/wiki/sp=
aces/ERPGT/pages/40934604889/Case+Escalation+-+Technical+Requirements+and+D=
esign#CE_TR04%3A-Escalation-Notification-Email-Template" local-id=3D"ee3ed2=
f1c56c" rel=3D"nofollow">https://datacomgroup.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/ERP=
GT/pages/40934604889/Case+Escalation+-+Technical+Requirements+and+Design#CE=
_TR04%3A-Escalation-Notification-Email-Template</a> )</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca863b15f9c4">
<p local-id=3D"fb818886d7e9">Get the Email Subject and Email Body</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2fa772f6ab10">
<p local-id=3D"1e8392d7d50d">Inject the escalation message to email body</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"010f3a47622d">
<p local-id=3D"d657d38ee8b7">Send the Email to the internal escalatee</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"56db59cd9dcc">
<p local-id=3D"fd4b304990c7">Add the message to Case&gt;Communication&gt;Me=
ssages</p></li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"df659d68058a"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9e68dbdf-be7d-4d32-95d8-c172a436fea8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"caddc9f32c19">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h5 local-id=3D"7513d8d2f969" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-MapReduceScript[OPTIONAL]"><span data-colorid=3D"nxoduv593m">Map Red=
uce Script [OPTIONAL]</span></h5>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"8e=
7a9677cca6" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col style=3D"width: 583.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 177.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3d94c6c7-2874-4ab8-9f4c-1575e40d8505">
<th class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTh"></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"5ec03026-8184-48a9-a=
9e3-2066948a69ae" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"0bf28de0316c"><strong>Description</strong></p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"304074b8-9f68-426a-8=
1f0-c193c002c92a" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"45889fa0fe40"><strong>Jira</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"45da221e-1da8-42f6-86d8-71ce42836279">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd">1</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e49ef208-f01c-485c-9778-a5ce0994c309" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<h4 local-id=3D"07d05661885e" id=3D"CaseEscalation-TechnicalRequirementsand=
Design-CE_TR07:RecoveryscripttoUpdatesCaseRecordstatusfieldwhencaseisescala=
tedandde-escalated">CE_TR07: Recovery script to Updates Case Record status =
field when case is escalated and de-escalated</h4>
<p local-id=3D"f5ab532ab607"><strong>Type</strong>: Map Reduce Script</p>
<p local-id=3D"ab406c423572"><strong>Purpose</strong>:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"81a82c63-7521-48ed-823d-99bd719c7688">
<li local-id=3D"ec347cd7-19d9-4c97-9e8d-53489f203a6e">
<p local-id=3D"fce9f150c606">In case the workflow action script fails there=
 is a optional map reduce to:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"4d2ef80598ad">
<li local-id=3D"6a97c8ed-32b0-4adf-a34a-543d5b0ad380">
<p local-id=3D"0118fe526554">Set the Parent Case Record to =E2=80=9CEscalat=
ed=E2=80=9D if atleast one of the child case escalation records is set to e=
scalated status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3cb62803-1048-4810-ba5b-37269043afa0">
<p local-id=3D"ec4d5d5b27ff">Set the Parent Case Record to =E2=80=9CIn Prog=
ress=E2=80=9D if only all of the child case escalation records are set to D=
e-escalated status.</p></li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"1195f7a6220d"><strong>Deploy</strong>: Scheduled every 15 mi=
nutes</p>
<p local-id=3D"cd2bf4731449"></p>
<p local-id=3D"84e6d0a17e1c"><strong>Logic</strong>:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"cafffdba-1f52-453e-a1e2-76dfaf539df7">
<li local-id=3D"1f78c497-9f85-4c26-9cec-d96564dac33e">
<p local-id=3D"9ba5285e4081">Get all case escalations grouped by the Parent=
_Case_Record.id</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"66d5d68b492b">
<p local-id=3D"78e28945f8fa">For each Parent Case records from #1 check if =
there are any child case escalation records with status=3D escalated.</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8eaffb4d42ea">
<li local-id=3D"d9cde71a63fd">
<p local-id=3D"f95e9917816e">If =E2=80=9CYes=E2=80=9D THEN</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"edacca7c9145">
<li local-id=3D"c2499ffe6df2">
<p local-id=3D"312ccda55188">IF Parent_Case_Record.Status !=3D =E2=80=9CEsc=
alated=E2=80=9D</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"89138ac3c83d">
<li local-id=3D"8fda05674d9f">
<p local-id=3D"0b84b9904485">Set Parent_Case_Record.satus =3D =E2=80=9CEsca=
lated=E2=80=9D</p></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"c314ef6f159a">
<p local-id=3D"0b0dc8e91017">If =E2=80=9CNo=E2=80=9D THEN</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"71bf7d14f69d">
<li local-id=3D"849fad92c57a">
<p local-id=3D"620020936ccb">IF Parent_Case_Record.Status =3D=3D =E2=80=9CE=
scalated=E2=80=9D</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d6c663cacb9c">
<li local-id=3D"bc53a877c846">
<p local-id=3D"9f12afc18cf2">Set Parent_Case_Record.satus =3D =E2=80=9CIn-P=
rogress=E2=80=9D</p></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"7dec169e055a"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"18a02a72-9284-4c18-92e7-a4345e614675" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"05248c87da73">&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"0b5010578613"></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
